http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/tamil-nadu/Award-for-three-schools/article14008828.ece

Minister for Forests M.S.M. Anandan gave away the ‘Best school awards’ of the State Government to three government schools in the district.They were: Corporation Middle School at '15 Velampalayam', Corporation Elementary School at Aramanaipudur, and Government Elementary School at Karikankattupudur.District Collector G. Govindaraj; district panchayat chairman M. Shanmugam; senior officials from Education Department; and elected representatives of Assembly, and civic bodies, were present.- Staff Reporter